'''佩佩·埃斯科巴'''（Pepe Escobar，{{bd|1954年||}}）是一名[[巴西|巴西]]記者<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pepe Escobar: "Bolsonaro é um paspalho útil com tempo de vida determinado"|url=https://www.brasil247.com/brasil/pepe-escobar-bolsonaro-e-um-paspalho-util-com-tempo-de-vida-determinado|accessdate=2021-01-30|date=2021-01-29|last=Sobreira|first=Leonardo|work=Brasil 247|language=pt-br|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208075422/https://www.brasil247.com/brasil/pepe-escobar-bolsonaro-e-um-paspalho-util-com-tempo-de-vida-determinado}}</ref>、[[地緣政治|地緣政治]]分析家。曾定期於[[亞洲時報在線|亞洲時報在線]]的專欄上撰寫有關[[中東|中東]]和[[亞洲|亞洲]]事務以及[[美国外交|美國外交政策]]的評論和文章。他也作為[[新聞評論員|新聞評論員]]出現在[[RT電視台|RT電視台]]、[[Press_TV|Press TV]]和[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]等電視台上<ref>{{cite news|title=Pepe Escobar on the U.S. Economic War Against Iran|url=https://www.foreignpolicyjournal.com/2013/02/19/pepe-escobar-on-the-u-s-economic-war-against-iran/|accessdate=2021-01-30|publisher=Foreign Policy Journal|date=2013-02-19|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021222824/https://www.foreignpolicyjournal.com/2013/02/19/pepe-escobar-on-the-u-s-economic-war-against-iran/}}</ref>。

自1990年代後期以來，他的工作主要聚焦於[[中亞|中亞]]、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]、[[中東|中東]]和[[伊朗|伊朗]]<ref>Sharma, Dinesh and Gielen, Uwe, "About the Contributors", ''The Global Obama: Crossroads of Leadership in the 21st Century'', Routledge 2013</ref>。

在2000年8月，埃斯科巴和另外兩名記者一度被[[塔利班|塔利班]]逮捕，被控拍攝[[足球比賽|足球比賽]]<ref>Dartnell, Michael York, ''Insurgency Online: Web Activism and Global Conflict'', University of Toronto Press, 2006, p. 56</ref>。

2022年4月，埃斯科巴的[[推特|推特]]帳號被停用，他認為這是[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|俄烏衝突]]期間[[西方世界|西方]]壓制異議聲音的一部分<ref>{{Cite web|title=West silencing dissenting voices to control narrative on Ukraine war|url=https://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2022/04/14/680320/Russia-conflict-Ukraine-dissenting-voices-|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2022-04-14|work=PressTV|language=En|archive-date=2022-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220509160018/https://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2022/04/14/680320/Russia-conflict-Ukraine-dissenting-voices-}}</ref>。埃斯科巴一貫批判西方國家對[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的立場<ref>{{Cite web|title=Twitter, gazeteci Pepe Escobar'ın hesabını engelledi|url=https://tr.sputniknews.com/20220414/twitter-gazeteci-pepe-escobarin-hesabini-engelledi-1055550016.html|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2022-04-14|work=Sputnik Türkiye|language=tr|archive-date=2022-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523172334/https://tr.sputniknews.com/20220414/twitter-gazeteci-pepe-escobarin-hesabini-engelledi-1055550016.html}}</ref>。

